{"id":689,"date":"2023-08-20T14:39:00","date_gmt":"2023-08-20T19:39:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/?p=689"},"modified":"2025-12-09T14:47:33","modified_gmt":"2025-12-09T20:47:33","slug":"alpha-tau-omega","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/posts\/2023\/2023\/alpha-tau-omega\/","title":{"rendered":"Alpha Tau Omega"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This is part of the <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"918\">Hazing Transparency Report<\/a>, which contains <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#terminology\">terminology definitions<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#rules\">rules defined<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-style-elevated is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fall 2023<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper grid-item-min-width-150 \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Incident: 8\/20\/2023<br>Location: Off Campus<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Reported: 8\/20\/2023<br>Reported by: GSU Staff, Hotline Report, Chapter Reported to NHQ<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Investigation: NHQ-led<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Description<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Alpha Tau Omega new members were made to engage in acts of personal servitude for active members and were forced\/coerced to consume alcohol. New members were subjected to demeaning acts and personal items were taken from them.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rules Violations<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Article III.A.(4) &#8211; Published Policies (Hazing)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Hazing: Consumption of Alcohol; Mental Health Threat; Lack of Access to Personal Items (Phones)<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary probation from 9\/12\/23-12\/13\/24<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Required educational sanctions, including, but not limited to 90% member completion of&nbsp;bystander intervention training<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Social probation until January 1, 2024 (per inter\/national organization) with new member-only, alcohol-free social events allowed until that time<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Required revision of new member education program<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Membership review (11 members removed)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Officer suspension and\/or removal<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Work with 3rd party consultant to review health and safety policies and practices&nbsp;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fall 2023 Description Alpha Tau Omega new members were made to engage in acts of personal servitude for active members and were forced\/coerced to consume alcohol. New members were subjected to demeaning acts and personal items were taken from them.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[5],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-689","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-5"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/689","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/